<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="10Janv1907"><font color="red">postmark 10 January 1907</font>, <cite>Selected Letters</cite> 143 (JJ to Stanislaus Joyce): Via Monte Brianzo, IV&deg;, Rome. <br>The other day I was thinking about my novel. How long am I at it now? Is there any use continuing it?</div>
